  <summary date="2019-04-18T20:17:40Z" status="Introduced in House">Transition to Independence Act of 2018

This bill directs the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to establish a demonstration program under which a state that has&#160;a Medicaid Buy-In&#160;program and meets other specified requirements may&#160;receive bonus payments for expanding employment opportunities for working-age individuals&#160;with disabilities who receive&#160;Medicaid-funded home- or community-based services.</summary>
